===Transitive verb===
'''to season''' ('''seasons''', '''seasoned''', '''seasoning''')

#<!--DefD--> to [[flavour]] [[food]] with [[spice|spices]], [[herb|herbs]] or [[salt]].
#<!--DefE--> to make [[fit]] for any use by time or habit; to [[habituate]]; to [[accustom]]; to [[inure]]; to [[ripen]]; to [[mature]]; as, to season one to a climate. 
#<!--DefH-->hence, to [[prepare]] by [[dry]]ing or [[harden]]ing, or [[removal]] of natural [[juice]]s; as, to season [[timber]]. 

